        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued March 31 at 3:17PM EDT until March 31 at 7:00PM EDT by NWS Columbia SC</headline>
        <description>SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 87 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 7 PM EDT THIS
EVENING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS

IN GEORGIA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 5 COUNTIES

IN EAST CENTRAL GEORGIA

BURKE                 COLUMBIA              LINCOLN
MCDUFFIE              RICHMOND

IN SOUTH CAROLINA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 10 COUNTIES

IN CENTRAL SOUTH CAROLINA

AIKEN                 BARNWELL              EDGEFIELD
FAIRFIELD             LANCASTER             LEXINGTON
MCCORMICK             NEWBERRY              RICHLAND
SALUDA

THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF AIKEN, AUGUSTA, BARNWELL,
BATESBURG-LEESVILLE, BLACKVILLE, CAYCE, CLARKS HILL, COLUMBIA,
EDGEFIELD, ELGIN, EVANS, JOHNSTON, LANCASTER, LANCASTER MILL,
LEXINGTON, LINCOLNTON, MARTINEZ, MCCORMICK, MURPHYS ESTATES,
NEWBERRY, NORTH AUGUSTA, OAK GROVE, RED BANK, RIDGE SPRING,
SALUDA, SEVEN OAKS, SPRINGDALE, THOMSON, WAYNESBORO,
WEST COLUMBIA, WILLISTON, WINNSBORO, AND WINNSBORO MILLS.
</description>
